title: Potential Presymptomatic Transmission of SARS-CoV-2, Zhejiang Province, China, 2020.

abstract: We report a 2-family cluster of persons infected with severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 in the city of Zhoushan, Zhejiang Province, China, during January 2020. The infections resulted from contact with an infected but potentially presymptomatic traveler from the city of Wuhan in Hubei Province.
